/////////////////////////////////////////////////

- ask input and output file names

- open input and output files

/////////////////////////////////////////////////

- m = read size of first set

- x = create array of size m

- read m values into x

/////////////////////////////////////////////////

- n = read size of second set

- y = create array of size n

- read n values into y

/////////////////////////////////////////////////

- finding union u

- u = create array of size m+n

- copy all values x into u

- copy only those values of y that are not in x into u

- p = count values in u

- print p

- print values of u

/////////////////////////////////////////////////

- finding intersection v

- v = create array of size m+n

- copy only those values of y that are in x into v

- q = count values in v

- print q

- print values of v

/////////////////////////////////////////////////






